<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA100">
<l>naṭakkiṟ paṭinaṭuṅku nōkkiṟ ṟicaivē</l>
<l>miṭikki ṉulakaṉaittu mēṅku - maṭukkaṟ</l>
<l>porumēṟō vāṉēṟō poṉṉoppāy niṉṉē</l>
<l>ṟurumēṟō voṉṟā vurai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If it walks, the earth trembles, if if looks the directions burn,</l>
<l>if it thunders that whole world is in panic. Is it a fighting bull</l>
<l>from the mountain, it is a cow bull, is it a thunder stroke</l>
<l>that is mounted by you who are like gold?, tell [me] for once.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
